Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.18,0:00:22.64,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,714)\blur3\fad(0,400}登山 要玩命吗！？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.61,0:00:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵 小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.07,0:00:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去爬哪座山
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.45,0:00:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还是从附近的山丘入门吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.37,0:00:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么不思进取
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.25,0:00:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定嫁不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.02,0:00:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟嫁人没关系吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.17,0:00:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说附近的山丘 就数——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.34,0:00:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.40,0:00:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登山都要带什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.73,0:00:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头盔？ 绳索？还要带储备粮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.11,0:00:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 至少要带些好吃的才行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.00,0:00:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫁不出去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.16,0:00:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 给你看看我的女人味
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.78,0:00:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(306,498)\3c&H000000&\bord3\shad0}1小时后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.16,0:00:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成 看着不错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还得给日向准备一份…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.83,0:00:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用剩渣随便弄弄就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:00:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.44,0:00:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么穿成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.14,0:01:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 怎么穿校服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.27,0:01:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇难了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还年轻不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吔 爬山了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.55,0:01:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 不许跑 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.53,0:01:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.79,0:01:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.33,0:01:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们今天要爬的天览山海拔197米
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.35,0:01:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比东京塔展望台还高47米！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.11,0:01:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\3c&H000000&\bord3\shad0\pos(130,12)}150米
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.87,0:01:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕 好担心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.45,0:01:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵快看 这朵蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.65,0:01:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿过树梢的阳光 好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这路比想象中的平常呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.22,0:01:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不到下面 一点不可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.48,0:01:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不危险
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.34,0:01:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 壁虎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.60,0:01:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.05,0:01:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登山有这么简单吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.28,0:01:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到山顶了吧 前面好明亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.44,0:01:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就山顶了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.51,0:02:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,视野真开阔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没爬很高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 秘密武器登场！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样装好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\bord3\shad0\pos(172,16)\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}燃烧口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord3\shad0\pos(182,274)}点火开关
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord3\shad0\pos(914,58)}火力调整阀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord3\shad0\pos(810,530)}燃料罐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.86,0:02:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锵 野营炊具炉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.51,0:02:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用它可以烧水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.28,0:02:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跟小葵在这里喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.10,0:02:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.22,0:02:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.16,0:02:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我做三明治了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.71,0:02:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你人不赖嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.57,0:02:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\pos(934,32)\shad0\bord3\c&H364E61&\3c&HCCD3D9&}边角下料
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.41,0:02:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃咯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也好~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来爬哪座山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.18,0:02:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 这就开始想下一座了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说 当然要去更漂亮的地方！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs32\blur3\3c&H252527&}行こう！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs32\blur3\3c&H252527&}スタッカートみたいに 胸を叩くワクワク感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs32\blur3\3c&H252527&}不思議　不安より
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs32\blur3\3c&H252527&}楽しみの容量が増えたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs32\blur3\3c&H252527&}また明日！やっほー
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs32\blur3\3c&H252527&}出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs32\blur3\3c&H252527&}昂扬感像断奏音符般拍打胸膛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs32\blur3\3c&H252527&}真奇妙 不但没有不安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs32\blur3\3c&H252527&}快乐的容量反而更大了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs32\blur3\3c&H252527&}明天再见！YAHOO
